title: Pro Evolution soccer 2012
description: Pro Evolution Soccer 2012 is the latest version of Konami's popular video game soccer franchise. This version is the 11th release in the series. Pro Evolution Soccer 2012 takes digital soccer to the next level by allowing you a wide range of game improvements over earlier versions to create the best and most realistic soccer game available to date. Some of the new features include improved teammate AI both on offense and defense, new off-the-ball controls, harder defensive assignments, and a new collision detection system. The improved teammate AI has become more true to life on defense and offense helping your team play more cohesively. The updated graphics in Pro Evolution Soccer 2012 improve movements, facial representations, and pitches.
